d check if `secondaryColor` is a legacy alias or a proper token.\n\nActually, lo
oking more carefully at the docs:\n- `DesignTokens.secondaryColor` is used in `S
wChatBubble` for system bubble text and status indicator. The docs don\'t explic
itly call it legacy, but they do say "禁止在新代码中使用" for Legacy aliases, an
d the only explicitly named legacy alias is `surfaceColor`. So this may not be a
blocking issue.\n\n2. **Blocking - `ImBloc` directly uses `DioClient` instead of
