**问题**: `_onConnect` 发射 `ImConnected()`，`_onDisconnect` 发射 `ImDisconnecte
d()`。这两个状态类不包含消息列表。`ChatPage` 的 `BlocConsumer` builder 仅在 `sta
te is ImMessagesLoaded || state is ImMessageSending || state is ImMessageSent ||
